				<span>Holy Crusade</span>
			</dt>
			<dd><div>Deals damage to enemies directly ahead,<br>and increases the user's max HP. If the user<br>is targeting an enemy and not using a skill<br>when their remaining shapeshift time runs out,<br>this skill will be used automatically, regardless<br>of whether or not the skill gauge is filled.</div><div class="skill-detail">Damage: 330 × 5 hits<br>Special Effects:<br>・HP +10%<br></div></dd></dl></div><div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png"></span><span>(Light) Strength +70%</span></dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Light: <br>increases strength by 70%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/1143744471e52c225083bf356743039b2.png"></span><span>(Light) Oath of the Righteous II</span></dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Light:<br>adds 30% to the modifier applied to damage<br>against shadow-attuned enemies and enemies<br>with no attunement for 45 seconds every time<br>the dragon gauge fills by 10%. This increase<br>will not stack, and, after activating, this ability<br>will not activate again for five seconds.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>・The stats shown here represent the dragon at maximum level, maximum bond, and fully unbound. They do not represent the stats when first obtained.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurer:</div><div>
