						<span>5</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</dt>
			<dd><div>Deals damage to enemies directly ahead,<br>and inflicts flashburn.</div><div class="skill-detail">Damage: 720 × 3 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 2,412<br>Skill Energy Required (Shared Skill): 9,678<br>Special Effects:<br>・Flashburn<br>　　Lasts 21 seconds<br>　　Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>　　Damage: 41.6<br></div></dd><dt
				>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/20cad8e4fa011f9a61e0e16c16dc42ba2.png"></span>
				<span>Lentus Oracle</span>
			</dt>
			<dd><div>Restores HP to the user, and grants<br>them the "Raphael's Embrace" effect.</div><div class="skill-detail">Recovery Potency: 90<br>Skill Energy Required: 9,360<br>Special Effects:<br>・Raphael's Embrace<br>　　Lasts 30 seconds<br>　　Critical Rate Increase: +15%<br>　　Knockback Immunity<br>　　Does not stack</div></dd></dl></div>
